  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Super Mahjong Taikai is a Miscellaneous game, published by Koei, which was released in Japan in 1992. It was also a view-limited Downloadable game for the Satellaview that was broadcast in at least 4 runs between June 29, 1997 and February 21, 1998.",
